    "parameters": [],
    "return_type": "",
    "exceptions": [],
    "description": {
      "es": "",
      "en": "Read a keypress and return the resulting character as a byte string. Nothing is echoed to the console. This call will block if a keypress is not already available, but will not wait for Enter to be pressed. If the pressed key was a special function key, this will return '\\000' or '\\xe0'; the next call will return the keycode. The Control-C keypress cannot be read with this function."
    },
